icontrol.drivers

Class GenericRS232

  • java.lang.Object
    • icontrol.drivers.Device
      • icontrol.drivers.GenericRS232

  • @iC_Annotation(CommPorts=RS232)
public class GenericRS232
extends Device
    Generic RS232 Instruments are registered in Dispatcher.RegisterDeviceClasses with this class as their Instrument-Class. Essentially all functionality to support generic RS232 Instruments is implemented in class Device.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    KPP (Kurt Pernstich: pernstich@alumni.ethz.ch)
